You can simply ask Alexa to control your “CTRL“, Such as: light”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “CTRL” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “CTRL” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “CTRL” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “CTRL” skill, and you'll be navigated to “CTRL” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking; 
Alexa turn on the Light; 
Alexa turn off the Light;
